 - Fix RINIT srand
 - Added json extension validation
 - All *Response classes, SolrDocument, SolrInputDocument are now final
 - All parameters functions throws SolrIllegalArgumentException instead of E_RROR
 - All SolrClient methods throws SolrClientExceptions instead of E_WARNING + SolrClientException
 - SolrClientExceptions messages are informative error messages in case of connection errors
 - SolrClient::system Access system servlet which fetch SolrServer info
 - SolrClient::commit argument $maxSegments is now DEPRECATED
 - Added support for expungeDeletes on SolrClient::commit

